description: Gourmet Pan Asian Grill Food Truck serving the Greater Tampa Bay Area.Using secret recipes from the Momma Mei's Little Red Cookbook, The I Wanna Wok Truck is leading the Great Culinary Leap Forward. Our food is inspired by the original street food of Asia - it's bold, spicy, unique, fast and delicious. We also offer authentic steamed Bao Buns that use the freshest ingredients - savory and addictive.
name: I Wanna Wok
